      <title>美联储古尔斯比预计劳动力市场稳定，利率下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-06/fed-s-goolsbee-sees-stable-labor-market-lower-rates-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[芝加哥联邦储备银行行长奥斯坦·古尔斯比表示，劳动力市场看起来基本稳定，预计一年后利率将“大幅下降”。古尔斯比在芝加哥联邦储备银行年度经济展望研讨会的炉边谈话中发表了讲话。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-06/fed-s-goolsbee-sees-stable-labor-market-lower-rates-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Dec 2024 17:07:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
